<note n="0761001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0761001">猶＝猛【元】</note>
<note n="0761002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0761002">杖＝仗【宋】【宮】，伏【聖】</note>
